                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On September 22, 1953, the United States Representative at the United Nations
                    opposed the Soviet proposal (United Nations document A/2484) for inscription on
                    the agenda of the Eighth Session of the General Assembly a reconsideration of
                    the Assembly’s resolution of August 28. In both the General (Steering) Committee
                    and the plenary session of the Assembly, the Soviet request for inscription was
                    defeated by large majorities. For the texts of Ambassador <persName
                        corresp="#p_LHCJ1">Lodge</persName>’s statements on this question, see
                    Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, October 5, 1953, pages
                    469–470.</p>
            </div>
